frames.caption: A young boy walks barefoot along a narrow, illuminated stone path suspended in a misty, cavernous environment. The path is lined with glowing lights, creating a mystical atmosphere as it winds through the dark, rocky landscape. The boy appears to be on a journey, surrounded by an ethereal blue glow.
frames.description: The scene depicts a surreal and mystical setting where a young boy is traversing a stone path that seems to float in a foggy, cavernous space. The path is illuminated by glowing lights, adding to the dreamlike quality of the environment.

frames.caption: A young boy stands on a narrow, illuminated stone path suspended in a misty, cavernous landscape. The path curves into the distance, surrounded by towering rock walls and a mysterious, glowing atmosphere.
